        "I am writing this letter to check my belongings which I  left during my stay. My name is Vishak V S  I stayed in your hotel from 15/07/2022 to 17/07/2022 in room number 207. I vacated the room on 17/07/2022 morning and after reaching home I realized that one of my Shirts and belt  had been left behind.",
